body:
• We the Critical Role fjandom have a meme of putting j’s in wjords to make it Fjord-related
  • There’s also the jeans meme (jeme) of putting a j in front of words to make it Denim™
  • Therefore, I present a perhaps inevitable concept: Jeans Fjord

blog.description:
Tumblr user happikattwuzheere does fanfictiony things.  

Drabble requests are cool, just keep in mind I might never get to them - if I get ideas from it, I'll write it, and if not, then oh well.  Just drop requests in the ask box and I'll do my best!

Fandom(s) I'm currently writing for:
Digimon Frontier, Homestuck  | Fandoms I might write for: Probably too many to list here; I love anything with fantasy elements, so if you have a particular fandom in mind, feel free to ask if it's something I'd be interested in doing drabbles/fics for!

summary: I’ve never really thought about the age range in the Critrole community but like it’s kinda crazy. Like last night before talks...
body: I’ve never really thought about the age range in the Critrole community but like it’s kinda crazy. Like last night before talks I was chillin in chat and people were talking about the Stephen one shot and this guy was like “as an 80’s kid it made me so happy”. And like, I had never really thought about the age range until then but it’s crazy. Like there are parents in this community and I’m over here stressing about junior year starting like wtf
